 "overview": "\u003Cp\u003ESpotlight is a SaaS solution that combines the power of social network communications with the efficiency of Agile project management. \u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003EBuilt upon a lean task management system, Spotlight differs from other task management tools because it focuses on people. Spotlight is the innovative creation of Vincent Serpico, who has built several task management systems from the ground up and has managed numerous virtual teams. Built out of necessity for his near-shore development company, serpicodev.com, Spotlight is a real-world tool built and used by folks who develop software and work virtually every day. \u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003ESpotlight brings virtual teams together in an interactive, social-centric UI. Leveraging familiar social tenants, such as short tweets and wall posts, Spotlight facilitates communication among team members in a fun and engaging way. Project managers, scrum masters and team leads can quickly and easily digest real-time status and availability updates from their whole team\u2026 on the web or on the go via the mobile app. Clients love Spotlight because it gives them a quick and easy way to assess the progress of their project at any time via consolidated project statistics and daily scrum updates. \u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003ECheck out Spotlight today at http://www.spotlightppm.com, and see why everyone agrees, \u201cSpotlight is the best app to manage virtual project teams\u201d. \u003C/p\u003E",
